        See the LICENSE file for details.
        
        .. _hard links: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hard_link
        .. _junctions: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NTFS_junction_point
        .. _ctypes: http://docs.python.org/library/ctypes.html
        
